divs: Sighting Detailswas standing in my friends front yard , look to the south , seen a yellow star didnt pay it know mind until my friend came outside and seen it , it was moving north fast , we got the rifle out of the truck it has a high power scope , look at it , it had no strobes no light at all , it had a fireball on it ass , wobbled as it flew by ,we watched it heading north until we could no longer see it, i thought i herd a rocket thats why i thought nasa had launch the shuttle but they didnt . to me it kinda look like a ICBM flying except for the wobbley flight.this make my third sighting.
